<p>Seventeen&nbsp;schools&nbsp;did not report this data to the Princeton Review:&nbsp; Albany, Appalachian,&nbsp;Charleston, CUNY, Florida International, Iowa, Kansas, Minnesota, Northern Illinois, Phoenix, Rutgers-Camden, South Texas, St. Thomas (Minneapolis), SUNY-Buffalo,&nbsp;Touro, UNLV, and Yale.</p>
<p dir="ltr">Unfortunately, the Princeton Review did not release the response rate per school, so it is impossible to determine how the rankings are affected by each school's representation among the respondents.</p>
