<a id="a6a00d8341c4eab53ef0147e0d2ec72970b"></a>


<h3>TaxProf Blog Weekend Roundup</h3>


<strong>Saturday</strong>:
<ul>
<li><a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/12/kleinbard-.html" target="_blank">Kleinbard:&nbsp; <em>The Health Care Law Is Constitutional (Still)</em></a></li>
