<h3>Top 5 Tax Paper Downloads</h3>


<a style="float: left;" onclick="window.open( this.href, '_blank', 'width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0' ); return false" href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4eab53ef01156fadc215970c-popup"><img class="at-xid-6a00d8341c4eab53ef01156fadc215970c " style="margin: 0px 5px 5px 0px;" title="SSRN" src="http://taxprof.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4eab53ef01156fadc215970c-800wi" border="0" alt="SSRN" /></a>This week's list of the&nbsp;<a href="http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/topten/topTenResults.cfm?groupingId=305496&amp;netorjrnl=ntwk">Top 5 Recent Tax Paper Downloads</a>&nbsp;is the same as last week's list:
<blockquote dir="ltr">
<p>1.&nbsp; [413 Downloads]&nbsp; <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/11/donaldson-.html" target="_blank">2010 Federal Tax Update</a>, by <a href="http://www.law.washington.edu/directory/profile.aspx?ID=95" target="_blank">Samuel A. Donaldson</a> (U. Washington)</p>
<p>2.&nbsp; [313 Downloads]&nbsp; <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/11/willis-chung.html" target="_blank">Oy Yes, the Healthcare Penalty is Unconstitutional</a>,&nbsp;by <a href="http://www.law.ufl.edu/faculty/willis/" target="_blank">Steven J. Willis</a> (Florida) &amp;&nbsp;<a href="http://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/cf_dev/AbsByAuth.cfm?per_id=1466372" target="_blank">Nakku Chung</a> (J.D. 2010, Florida)</p>
<p>3.&nbsp; [287 Downloads]&nbsp; <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/10/kaplan-.html" target="_blank">Financing Long-Term Care After Health Care Reform</a>,&nbsp;by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.law.uiuc.edu/faculty-admin/directory/RichardKaplan" target="_blank">Richard L. Kaplan</a> (Illinois)</p>
<p>4.&nbsp; [265 Downloads]&nbsp; <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/12/polsky-sophisticated-roth-conversion-planning.html" target="_blank">High Volatility, Negative Correlation, Roth IRA Conversions, and the Codified Economic Substance Doctrine</a>, by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.law.unc.edu/faculty/directory/polskygreggd/" target="_blank">Gregg D. Polsky</a> (North Carolina)</p>
<p>5.&nbsp; [231 Downloads]&nbsp; <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/10/abrams-did-.html" target="_blank">Did Codification of Economic Substance Repeal the Partnership Anti-Abuse Rule?</a>, by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.law.emory.edu/faculty/faculty-profiles/howard-e-abrams.html" target="_blank">Howard Abrams</a> (Emory)</p>
</blockquote>



