<a id="a6a00d8341c4eab53ef0148c6ca3de7970c"></a>


<h3>IRS Enforcement Actions Disproportionately Hit Minority Areas </h3>


<a href="http://www.taxlifeboat.com/articles_FullStudy.php" target="_blank">IRS Enforcement’s Impact on Minority Communities</a>, by Thomas M. Evans:
<blockquote>
<p>Areas with large African-American and Hispanic populations are subjected to IRS enforcement actions at double the rate of the general population, according to a new analysis. ...Although African-Americans comprised 12.3% of the U.S. population in 2000, they represent 22.0% of the total population of the top 1,000 zip codes with IRS liens. Similarly, while Hispanics accounted for 12.5% of the total population in 2000, they accounted for 24.4% of the population in the zip codes with the highest number of IRS tax liens.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>(Hat Tip: <a href="http://www.accountingtoday.com/news/IRS-Enforcement-Actions-Hit-Minority-Areas-Harder-56566-1.html" target="_blank">Web CPA</a>.)</p>



<!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->
<div><script type="text/javascript">var addthis_pub="paulcaron";</script><a href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php" onmouseover="return addthis_open(this, '', encodeURIComponent('http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/12/irs-enforcement.html'), encodeURIComponent('IRS Enforcement Actions Disproportionately Hit Minority Areas '));" onmouseout="addthis_close()" onclick="return addthis_sendto()" title="Bookmark and Share" target="_blank"><img src="http://s7.addthis.com/static/btn/lg-share-en.gif" width="125" height="16" alt="Bookmark and Share" style="border:0"/></a><script type="text/javascript" src="http://s7.addthis.com/js/200/addthis_widget.js"></script></div>
<!-- AddThis Button END -->

<p class="posted">
December 16, 2010 in <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/irs_news/">IRS News</a>, <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/tax/">Tax</a>  | <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/12/irs-enforcement.html">Permalink</a>

| <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/12/irs-enforcement.html#comments">Comments (3)</a>


