<h3>Borden: <em> The Prince and the Paupers -- A Tax Fable</em></h3>


<a href="http://www.brooklaw.edu/faculty/directory/facultymember/biography.aspx?id=brad.borden" target="_blank">Bradley T. Borden</a> (Brooklyn),&nbsp;<a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/bradley-t-borden/the-prince-and-the-pauper_1_b_796745.html" target="_blank">The Prince and the Paupers:&nbsp;A Tax Fable</a>:
<blockquote><p>The recent tax deal brings to mind a fable that I've told my young daughter to explain the current tax system.</p></blockquote>




