December 14, 2010 in <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/political_news/">Political News</a>, <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/tax/">Tax</a>  | <a href="http://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2010/12/rahm-emanuel-.html">Permalink</a>

